STATE
v.
Jessie A. MOORE. No. 95P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 6, 2006. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Kristy M. Newton, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st day of February 2006 by Defendant for "Notice of Appeal for Discretionary Review":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of April 2006."
